and Channel 1 Frost.","flavorText":"Sweet!","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"id":"BlueHedgehog:ClassicModeRelic","name":"Classic Mode","tier":"Special","pool":"Hedgehog_blue25","description":"If you take 2+ damage, exhaust ALL of your Rings.","flavorText":"Aw yeah! This is happening!","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"id":"BlueHedgehog:LimiterRingRelic","name":"Limiter Ring","tier":"Special","pool":"Hedgehog_blue25","description":"When you play a Trick, gain 1 less Vigor.","flavorText":"Don't sweat it! Anyways, no adventure is fun if it's too easy, right?","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"id":"BlueHedgehog:StampRelic","name":"Stamp","tier":"Special","pool":"Hedgehog_blue25","description":"You may right-click this relic to remove your offclass card from the Chao Garden event.","flavorText":"Meme! Approved.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"id":"BlueHedgehog:ChaoThreeRelic","name":"Three Chao","tier":"Special","pool":"Hedgehog_blue25","description":"Start each combat with 2 additional Orb slots.","flavorText":"Don't worry little buddy.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"id":"BlueHedgehog:CDFutureRelic","name":"Time Warp - Future","tier":"Special","pool":"Hedgehog_blue25","description":"At the start of combat, lose 1 Level Up Speed. Increase your max hand size by 3. When you create a Ring, randomize its cost.","flavorText":"Inflation.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"id":"BlueHedgehog:CDPastRelic","name":"Time Warp - Past","tier":"Special","pool":"Hedgehog_blue25","description":"If you take 3 damage, Exhaust ALL Rings in your hand.","flavorText":"Golden Era.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"id":"BlueHedgehog:BlueQuillPlusRelic","name":"Blue Quill+","tier":"Boss","pool":"Hedgehog_blue25","description":"Replaces Blue Quill. At the start of combat, add 3 Shortcuts to your hand.","flavorText":"Talk about low budget flights!","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"id":"BlueHedgehog:RingEnergyBonusRelic","name":"Ring Energy Bonus","tier":"Boss","pool":"Hedgehog_blue25","description":"For every 3 Rings at the start of your turn, gain 1 [E] .","flavorText":"Wow, where does somebody put all those gold rings?","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"id":"BlueHedgehog:FireSoulRelic","name":"Fire Soul","tier":"Shop","pool":"Hedgehog_blue25","description":"When you use a Crest of Fire or a Strike card, first gain 1 Block. This amount permanently increases when you enter a Rest Site.","flavorText":"WOW! The wisdom of Sinbad of the Seven Seas! The adventurer of adventurers!","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"}],"potions":[{"id":"BlueHedgehog:PowerCorePotion","name":"Power Core","rarity":"Common","description":"Add a Cost 0 Ring to your hand and choose between Level Up Speed, Flight, and Power.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"id":"BlueHedgehog:ChaosSodaPotion","name":"Chaos Soda","rarity":"Uncommon","description":"Exhaust up to 1 card. Add 1 Trick+ that costs 0 to your hand. Gain 1 Orb slot. Enter Calm.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"id":"BlueHedgehog:SlowPotion","name":"Ice Cannon","rarity":"Rare","description":"Apply Slow to ALL enemies.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"}],"creatures":[{"id":"Sonic","name":"The Hedgehog","type":"Player","minHP":"68","maxHP":"75","minHPA":"64","maxHPA":"71","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"id":"ModLagavulin","name":"Lagavulin","type":"Elite","minHP":"109","maxHP":"111","minHPA":"112","maxHPA":"115","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"}],"keywords":[{"name":"ALL","description":"ALL, in this case, refers to Draw, Discard, Hand, and Exhaust Piles.\n\nPerfected Strike and Hermit's Grudge do NOT look at the Exhaust pile.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"name":"This is displayed in the tooltip.","description":"This is displayed in the tooltip. Spaces should not be used be avoided in NAMES, with the exception of multi-word keywords (see next entry).","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"name":"More tips","description":"names strings should be all lowercase. Use case goes like this: BlueHedgehog:Trick","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"name":"Crest of Fire","description":"If Fatal, upgrade ALL Crest of Fire cards in your deck permanently. Crest of Fire cards can be upgraded any number of times.\n\nAfter upgrading more than 7 times, take 1 damage per upgrade. For example, Fire Tackle+10 will hurt you for 3 damage.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"name":"Dizzy","description":"Target deals damage reduced by the cost of the highest card in your hand.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"name":"Precious","description":"Retain. If Exhausted, enter Wrath.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"name":"Echo Form","description":"The first card you play each turn is played twice.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"name":"Flame Barrier","description":"When you are attacked this turn, deal X damage to the attacker.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"name":"Flip","description":"Cost 3+ -> Cost 0\nCost 2 -> Cost 1\nCost 1 -> Cost 2\nCost 0 -> Cost 3","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"name":"Friend","description":"At the end of combat, you may choose between keeping Assist or the new generated card.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"name":"HotRod","description":"If you haven't played any cards, gain 5(6) Block.\nIf you have played 1 card, gain 7(8) Block.\nIf you have played 2 cards, gain 10(12) Block AND deal 6(8) damage.\nIf you have played 2+ cards, gain 3(4) Block.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"name":"If Center","description":"If this card is at the Center of your hand, activate the extra effect. Ignore Rings for this condition.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"name":"If Leftmost","description":"If this card is at the very left of your hand, activate the extra effect. Ignore Rings for this condition.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"name":"If Most Left Or Right","description":"If this card is at the very left or right of your hand, activate the extra effect. Ignore Rings for this condition.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"name":"If Rightmost","description":"If this card is at the very right of your hand, activate the extra effect. Ignore Rings for this condition.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"name":"If Not Most Left","description":"If this card is NOT at the very left of your hand, activate the extra effect. Ignore Rings for this condition.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"name":"Level Up","description":"If you haven't played anything or your last card played was a Skill, Rings in your hand increase your Block by 1.\nIf your last card played was an Attack, Rings in your hand increase your damage by 1.\nIf your last card played was a Power, Rings in your hand increase your Focus by 1.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"name":"LSD","description":"This turn, Rings heal 1 HP instead of giving you Temporary HP. If Rings were already in your hand, they heal 3 HP.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"name":"Multiword Keyword","description":"Make sure the first element in NAMES has no underscores. The rest should use _ in the place of spaces. In card text, you'll use the underscore versions.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"name":"Rev","description":"Alias for \"triggering the passive effect of an orb.\" Unless explicitly specified, probably refers to the rightmost Orb slot.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"name":"Ring","description":"While this is in your hand, increase Block gained from cards by 1.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"name":"Spin Up","description":"When you play this card, increase its cost by 1. Any modifications to cost persist for the rest of combat. If randomized, lower the randomized cost by 1.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"},{"name":"Trick","description":"You should not see this message.","mod":"The Hedgehog, Sonic"}],"mods":[{"name":"The Hedgehog, Sonic","version":"1.0.0","authors":["SpireWolf25"],"credits":"","description":"Brings Sonic the Hedgehog to Slay the Spire.\n\r\nGameplay\n- Collect Rings to build your Dexterity\n- Perform Tricks to gain Vigor\n\r\nFeatures\n- BLAST PROCESSING\n- 75+ cards\n- Voice Clips (can be disabled in config)\n- Music (can be disabled in config. Will not play for other characters)","mts_version":"3.30.0","sts_version":"12-18-2022","dependencies":["basemod","stslib"],"optional_dependencies":[]}]}